ISLAMABAD, Dec 19 (APP):Minister of State for Information and Broadcasting Farrukh Habib said on Sunday that Prime Minister Imran Khan during his address to OIC Foreign Ministers Conference called on the world community to take immediate steps to address the humanitarian crisis in Afghanistan.
In a tweet, he said that the Prime Minister presented the case of Muslims on Islamophobia including Kashmir and Palestine issues in detail.
